    <searchtitle>NHS Business Definition: Employment Status Questionnaire - Description</searchtitle>
  </titlealts>
  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_employment_status_questionnaire">Employment Status Questionnaire</xref>
 is a type of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_assessment_tool">ASSESSMENT TOOL</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
The 
              <xref outputclass="businessDefinition"
               keyref="business_definition_employment_status_questionnaire">Employment Status Questionnaire</xref>
 consists of three questions relating to the 
              <xref outputclass="dataSet"
               keyref="dataset_improving_access_to_psychological_therapies_data_set">Improving Access to Psychological Therapies Data Set</xref>
 from which the 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_employment_status">EMPLOYMENT STATUS</xref>, 
              <xref outputclass="attribute"
               keyref="attribute_statutory_sick_pay_receipt_indicator">STATUTORY SICK PAY RECEIPT INDICATOR</xref>
 and benefit status of the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 can be derived.        </p>
  </div>
